title: Pixel 3a IP Address issues to work with Android Studio
content:
Hello Dear Pixel Community, I'm currently having an issue with finding an IP address on Pixel 3a...
I know where exactly it is...but it shows MAC address instead of IP address I want...
Reason: Trying to connect my pixel 3a with Android Studio for Wireless ADB...
Laptop: Macbook Pro with Catalina 10.15.1
